       dashboard.([https://github.com/fuzzymannerz/swmp]Source Code)
     * [http://www.thruk.org/]Thruk - Multibackend monitoring web
       interface with support for Naemon, Nagios, Icinga and Shinken.
     * [https://uchiwa.io/]Uchiwa - Simple dashboard for sensu.
     * [https://github.com/Netflix/vector/]Vector - An on-host performance
       monitoring framework.
     * [https://www.xymon.com/]Xymon - Network monitoring inspired by Big
       Brother.
     * [http://www.zabbix.com/]Zabbix - Enterprise-class software for
       monitoring of networks and applications.
     * [http://community.zenoss.org/]Zenoss - Application, server, and
